       A Drop in the Ocean - a Compact Disc by Kevan and Gareth Craft.

     `A Drop in the Ocean' is a limited pressing of only 1000 copies and
     in purchasing  the Compact Disc,  not only have you  an opportunity
     to collect this rare recording but you'll also be able to listen to
     a slice of Amiga music history from musicians who also happen to be
     Amiga musicians JUST LIKE YOURSELF!

     Yes, despite what  some "boring fart" critics have said, 'A Drop in
     the Ocean' CD by The Craft Brothers was recorded and produced using
     an Amiga 500 Plus, in a their own BEDROOM  home studio environment!
     Forget $40 Million record deals for  the likes  of Michael Jackson,
     forget Ł500,000 studio  costs for Pop bands  such as Blur and Oasis
     and experience a CD with a collection of songs and instrumentals by
     Amiga users and musicians who put together the project themselves!

     'A Drop in the Ocean' CD by Amiga enthusiasts for Amiga enthusiasts!

                    Open your ears to the possibilities!!!!
               A Drop in the Ocean. definitely recommended.


